<%= form_for @doctor, :url => { :action => "create" } do |f|%>      
<div class="container  pt-3"> 
		<div class="card">
			<div class="card-header p-3 container-fluid">
				<div class="row">
					<h3 class="col-md-9">Add Doctor</h3> 
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card-body">
				<div>   
	  				<p>   
					  <div class="form-group">   
							<label>Doctor Name</label>   
							<%= f.text_field :name, :required => true, class:"form-control"%>   
					  </div>   

					  <div class="form-group">   
				      <label>Email</label>   
				      <%= f.email_field :email, :required => true, class:"form-control" %>   
					  </div>   

					  <div class="form-group">   
					    <label>Password</label>   
				      <%= f.password_field :password, :required => true, class:"form-control" %>
					  </div> 
					  <div class="form-group">   
					     <label>Registration no.</label>   
					        <%= f.number_field :registration_no, :required => true, class:"form-control" %>   
					  </div> 
					  <div class="form-group">   
					     <label>Speciality</label>   
					        <%= f.text_field :speciality, :required => true, class:"form-control" %>   
					  </div> 
					  <div class="form-group">   
					     <label>Consultancy Fee</label>   
					        <%= f.number_field :consultancy_fee, :required => true, class:"form-control" %>   
					  </div>   
				  </p>   
				</div> 
		</div> 
		<div class="card-footer p-3 container-fluid">
			<div class="row d-flex justify-content-md-end">
				<div class="col-md-3 d-flex justify-content-md-end">
		  		<%= f.submit 'Save' , class: "btn btn-primary "%>   
				<%= link_to 'Cancel', { controller: 'doctors', action: 'index'} , class: "btn btn-secondary ", style:"margin-left: 1em"%>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div> 
</div> 
<% end %>   
